Up she goes.

1092
02:20:32,307 --> 02:20:34,142
Ain't got no spit.

1093
02:20:53,328 --> 02:20:56,456
Try and keep him off me until I'm lower.

1094
02:20:59,959 --> 02:21:01,961
Okay, okay, I'm ready.

1095
02:24:42,349 --> 02:24:46,978
Bring him up, goddamn it.
Bring him up now!

1096
02:24:53,985 --> 02:24:56,154
Pull it up. Pull it.

1097
02:25:09,376 --> 02:25:12,045
Come on, Quint, bring him in.

1098
02:25:16,049 --> 02:25:17,759
It's giving way.

1099
02:25:32,774 --> 02:25:35,110
Rig something!

1100
02:25:39,447 --> 02:25:40,699
Got it?

1101
02:25:45,662 --> 02:25:47,163
It's comin'.

1102
02:25:50,458 --> 02:25:51,626
Slower.

1103
02:29:55,495 --> 02:29:57,414
Show me the tank.

1104
02:30:20,395 --> 02:30:21,688
Blow up!

1105
02:30:26,026 --> 02:30:28,236
Smile, you son of a bitch!

1106
02:32:19,889 --> 02:32:21,266
Quint?

1107
02:32:22,809 --> 02:32:24,185
No.

1108
02:32:35,947 --> 02:32:38,074
Can we get in on those?

1109
02:32:46,541 --> 02:32:48,293
What day is this?

1110
02:32:51,004 --> 02:32:54,299
It's Wednesday. It's Tuesday, I think.

1111
02:32:56,384 --> 02:32:58,678
I think the tide's with us.

1112
02:32:59,846 --> 02:33:01,639
Keep kicking.

1113
02:33:05,935 --> 02:33:08,104
I used to hate the water.

1114
02:33:11,358 --> 02:33:13,276
I can't imagine why.

